    {
      "acf_fc_layout": "block_text_fh",
      "title": "Welcome to North Shore Orthodontics",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "text": "Welcome to North Shore Orthodontics, a respected provider of orthodontics in the Whitestone, NY community. Our practice’s top priority is to provide you the highest quality orthodontic care in a friendly, comfortable environment. Dr. Efraim Zak, Dr. Scott Friedman, and Dr. Randy Weinstein utilize the latest technological advancements to give you the beautiful smile you deserve."
        },
        {
          "text": "At North Shore Orthodontics, we make sure you receive the most effective care possible. Our treatment options include traditional metal braces, Invisalign<sup>®</sup> clear aligners, Clarity™ ceramic brackets, Empower® braces, PROPEL® Orthodontics and Brava Lingual Braces. We recognize that you have unique needs, and we take pride in creating a treatment plan that is right for you. Whether you’re an adult, adolescent or child, our knowledgeable doctors and staff are committed to making you smile! Contact our Whitestone orthodontic office to schedule an appointment today."
        }
      ],
